to gossip about this,

164
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,879
be prepared to face my sword

165
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:33,480
and misfortune.

166
00:08:34,180 --> 00:08:36,620
♪Whose silhouette♪

167
00:08:36,620 --> 00:08:39,860
♪Appears near, then far♪

168
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:42,759
Go home.

169
00:08:47,279 --> 00:08:48,080
Come home with me.

170
00:08:49,580 --> 00:08:53,300
